A '''Bye-Fellow''' is a position in [[academia]] and [[post-secondary education]] at several [[United Kingdom|British]] and [[Commonwealth of Nations|Commonwealth]] universities for a [[Fellow]] who is not a member of the foundation of a college, or "may or may not have fewer privileges when compared to a full fellow".<ref>University of Cambridge, [http://janus.lib.cam.ac.uk/db/node.xsp?id=Glossary%2FBye-Fellow Glossary: Bye-Fellow], ''Janus''. Retrieved August 12, 2015.</ref>
